content:
Map Responses to Email Summary Fields

To store Einstein's responses, map them to fields on the EmailMessage and Case objects.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Edit on records
OR
Modify All Data

From Map Responses to Salesforce Fields, in the Work Summaries Setup page, select Edit.
For the Individual Email Summary and Combined Summary, select the EmailMessage and Case fields where you want to map each output. To ensure that fields can hold the entire summary, we recommend mapping summaries to fields with a long text format. Each field must have a different name.

Click Save.

WARNING: We don't recommend changing the field mappings after you set them up.

Activate Work Summaries for Email
title: Configuring Einstein Email Summaries in Service Cloud
